OL,3,C#19 million community diagnostic
OL,4,Ccentre coming to West Cumbria
OL,6,FWork has begun to create a #19 million
OL,7,Fcommunity diagnostic centre in the
OL,8,Fheart of Workington town.
OL,10,FThe new centre is set to have MRI, CT,
OL,11,FX-ray and ultrasound scanning
OL,12,Ffacilities to help speed up diagnoses
OL,13,Fin the region.
OL,15,FThe trust say referrals to diagnostic
OL,16,Fservices in north Cumbria have doubled
OL,17,Fover the past three years which has
OL,18,Fled to longer waiting times.
