OL,3,C#19 million community diagnostic
OL,4,Ccentre coming to West Cumbria
OL,6,FThe North Cumbria Integrated Care NHS
OL,7,FFoundation Trust (NCIC) has been
OL,8,Fproviding temporary mobile units at
OL,9,Fthe Cumberland Infirmary and West
OL,10,FCumberland Hospital to try and reduce
OL,11,Fwaiting.
OL,13,FIt's hoped the new Community
OL,14,FDiagnostic centre will offer a more
OL,15,Fpermanent solution to reduce
OL,16,Ftravelling and waiting times for
OL,17,Fdiagnoses.
