OL,3,C#19 million community diagnostic
OL,4,Ccentre coming to West Cumbria
OL,6,FDr Madu Varma, Clinical Director of
OL,7,Fspeciality medicine and consultant
OL,8,Fcardiologist, said: "We are all
OL,9,Fdelighted that work has now started to
OL,10,Fbuild the new centre.
OL,12,F"By providing more diagnostics, this
OL,13,Fwill help with quicker diagnoses of a
OL,14,Frange of conditions."
OL,16,F"When determining the location for the
OL,17,FCentre, we considered population
OL,18,Fdemand and health needs as well as
OL,19,Ftravel distance and access.
