OL,3,C#19 million community diagnostic
OL,4,Ccentre coming to West Cumbria
OL,6,F"Workington town centre is the ideal
OL,7,Flocation and is accessible via public
OL,8,Ftransport.
OL,10,F"With phase two of the redevelopment
OL,11,Fof West Cumberland Hospital due to
OL,12,Fcomplete this summer, this is another
OL,13,Ffantastic investment in health
OL,14,Fservices in the county."
OL,16,FThe foundations of the new building
OL,17,Fhave been laid and it's hoped the
OL,18,Fcentre will be up and running by
OL,19,Fsummer next year.
